      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SAIL AWAY SAM (3) has been without a win for a while, the latest jumping from an outside draw when fifth (23.63) at this track in a Grade 5. Form here sound including two wins. Can make amends. SIGHT AND SOUND (2) has not raced since scoring (29.91) over 515m at this track three months ago. Form here at the trip sound including two wins. Expected to feature on best form. IT'S A TEASE (1) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by one length at Maitland in a handy 22.56 beating Irinka Wayne. Has a strong record out of this box with three wins and a minor placing from four starts. Can continue on with her winning form. FASCINATE BAILEY (4) has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.",
